OL,3,CFly-tippers target Bristol lane just
OL,4,Cshort distance from legal dump site
OL,6,FTonnes of rubbish has been illegally
OL,7,Ffly-tipped along a lane in Bristol -
OL,8,Fjust a short distance from a legal
OL,9,Fwaste and refuse site.
OL,11,FITV News filmed images of the site
OL,12,Falong Kings Weston Lane in Avonmouth.
OL,14,FIt's said to include bed bases,
OL,15,Fpallets and plastic tanks - materials
OL,16,Fconnected to both residential and
OL,17,Fbusiness properties.
OL,19,FBristol City Council says officers
OL,20,Fhave been to the site and begun an
OL,21,Finvestigation.
