OL,6,FA spokesperson said it will be cleared
OL,7,Fas a priority: "Officers have assessed
OL,8,Fthe site and are now making
OL,9,Farrangements for the right equipment
OL,10,Fto be sent to clear this sizeable and
OL,11,Fillegal dumping of waste.
OL,13,F"Material that could link the waste to
OL,14,Fresidential and business addresses has
OL,15,Fbeen found and will now be analysed as
OL,16,Fpart of an investigation into the
OL,17,Fsource of this fly-tipping.
OL,19,F"If the opportunity arises to
OL,20,Fprosecute perpetrators we will not
OL,21,Fhesitate to act.
