OL,6,F"Flytipping like this is often linked
OL,7,Fto unlicensed waste carriers. It's
OL,8,Fimportant that anyone who is paying
OL,9,Fsomeone to take away their waste has
OL,10,Fappropriate licences in place and can
OL,11,Fproduce evidence of these licences
OL,12,Fwhen asked for it.
OL,14,F"Always ask your contractor to
OL,15,Fevidence their credentials before
OL,16,Fpaying for their services."
